          <b>„Äã** SankiRoBot Music VC Assistant ** „Ää</b>
            
 SankiRoBot Music VC Assistant plays plays music in your group's voice chat
 
 Assistant name >> @SankiAssistant
 
<b> Setting up </b>

1) Make bot admin
2) Start a voice chat
3) Try `/ytt [song name]` for the first time by an admin
*) If userbot joined enjoy music, If not add @SankiAssistant to your group and retry

<b> Commands </b>

=>> Song Playing üéß 
 
  /ytt: Play song using youtube music
  /play [yt url] : Play the given yt url
  /deezer: Play song via deezer
  /saavn: Play song via jio saavn
  
=>> Playback ‚èØ

  /skip: Skips the current track
  /pause: Pause track
  /resume: Resumes the paused track
  /end: Stops media playback
  Inline mode supported

*Player cmd and all other cmds except /pause, /skip, /resume, /end  are only for admins with manage group

